request.description:
### Get Provider Details

This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve provider details from the server.

#### Request Body

This request does not require a request body.

#### Response Body

- `providerId`: (string) The unique identifier of the provider.
    
- `name`: (string) The name of the provider.
    
- `email`: (string) The email address of the provider.
    
- `phone`: (string) The phone number of the provider.
    
- `address`: (string) The address of the provider.
